@layout DefaultLayout
@page "/portfolio/behaviour"
@{
    var openGraphModel = new OpenGraphModel()
    {
        Title = "Behaviour - Fydar",
        Description = "A complete node-based behaviour system.",
        CanonicalUrl = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio/behaviour",
        Properties = [
            new OpenGraphModelImage()
            {
                Url = "https://fydar.dev/media/header.webp",
                Alt = "A portrait of Fydar in an anime art style."
            }
        ]
    };
    var linkData = new LinkData()
    {
        new LinkDataBreadcrumbList()
        {
            new LinkDataBreadcrumbListItem()
            {
                Name = "Portfolio",
                Item = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio"
            },
            new LinkDataBreadcrumbListItem()
            {
                Name = "Behaviour",
                Item = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio/behaviour"
            }
        }
    };
}

<HeadContent>
    <OpenGraphComponent Model="@openGraphModel" />
    <LinkDataComponent Model="@linkData" />
</HeadContent>

<article class="page-behaviour">

    <div class="container">
        <Block_ArticleHeader>
            <h1 data-nosnippet>Behaviour</h1>
        </Block_ArticleHeader>

        <Block_ArticleIntroduction>
            <Sidebar>
                <Block_PillCloud>
                    <Pill_CSharp />
                </Block_PillCloud>

                <p>@openGraphModel.Description.Default</p>

                <menu class="externallinks" aria-label="Project External links">
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/fydar/RPGCore" target="_blank"><SvgSprite Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-github" Alt="GitHub" /></a></li>
                </menu>

                <ShareLink Url="@openGraphModel.CanonicalUrl.Html" />
            </Sidebar>
            <Container>
            </Container>
        </Block_ArticleIntroduction>

        <Block_ArticleOutlined>
            <Sidebar>
                <aside>
                    <Block_TableOfContents />
                </aside>
            </Sidebar>
            <Content>

                <OutlineSection Id="nodes" LinkName="Nodes">
                    <Block_ArticleHeading>
                        <hgroup>
                            <p>Designing the</p>
                            <h2>Nodes</h2>
                        </hgroup>
                    </Block_ArticleHeading>

                    <p>I've been wrestling with the design of the node API for a long time, with every iteration reducing it's complexity and taking advantage of the latest C# features. The most recent C# feature that I'm yet to take advantage of is <b>Source Generators</b>, which opens up the field of APIs massively.</p>

                    <p>With that said, here is the latest design of the Node API.</p>

                    <img decoding="async" class="media-wide" src="@Assets["media/behaviour/behaviour-nodeapi.svg"]" alt="The API for defining a Node." />

                    <Block_Callout Type="construction">
                        <Icon><SvgSprite Link="/icons.svg?v=1#fluent-emoji-high-contrast--construction" Alt="Check" /></Icon>
                        <ChildContent>This section of my website is currently <b>under construction</b>.</ChildContent>
                    </Block_Callout>

                </OutlineSection>

                <OutlineSection Id="graphs" LinkName="Graphs">
                    <Block_ArticleHeading>
                        <hgroup>
                            <p>Assembling some</p>
                            <h2>Graphs</h2>
                        </hgroup>
                    </Block_ArticleHeading>

                    <p>Now that we have some nodes, we can start assembling them into graphs. Here is the above Add node in a graph.</p>

                    <Block_NodeGraph TargetSize="640">

                        <Connection StartX="-8" StartY="-5" EndX="-5" EndY="-2" />
                        <Connection StartX="-8" StartY="0" EndX="-5" EndY="-1" />

                        <Connection StartX="3" StartY="-3" EndX="6" EndY="1" />
                        <Connection StartX="3" StartY="5" EndX="6" EndY="2" />
                        <Node X="-14" Y="-7" MinWidth="6">
                            <Name>Player Level</Name>
                            <Content>
                                <div class="graph-node-section-sockets">

                                    <div class="graph-node-outputs">
                                        <div class="graph-node-output connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-label">Level</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </Content>
                        </Node>
                        <Node X="-14" Y="-2" MinWidth="6">
                            <Name>Integer</Name>
                            <Content>
                                <div class="graph-node-section-sockets">

                                    <div class="graph-node-outputs">
                                        <div class="graph-node-output connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-label">Output</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </Content>
                        </Node>
                        <Node X="-5" Y="3" MinWidth="8">
                            <Name>Roll</Name>
                            <Content>
                                <div class="graph-node-section-sockets">

                                    <div class="graph-node-inputs">

                                        <div class="graph-node-input" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">Min</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="graph-node-input" style="--row: 2">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">Max</div>
                                        </div>

                                    </div>

                                    <div class="graph-node-outputs">
                                        <div class="graph-node-output connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-label">Value</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </Content>
                        </Node>
                        <Node X="-3" Y="-5" MinWidth="6">
                            <Name>Multiply</Name>
                            <Content>
                                <div class="graph-node-section-sockets">

                                    <div class="graph-node-inputs">

                                        <div class="graph-node-input connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">A</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="graph-node-input connected" style="--row: 2">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">B</div>
                                        </div>

                                    </div>

                                    <div class="graph-node-outputs">
                                        <div class="graph-node-output connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-label">Output</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </Content>
                        </Node>
                        <Node X="8" Y="-2" MinWidth="6">
                            <Name>Add</Name>
                            <Content>
                                <div class="graph-node-section-sockets">

                                    <div class="graph-node-inputs">

                                        <div class="graph-node-input connected" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">A</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="graph-node-input connected" style="--row: 2">
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-input-label">B</div>
                                        </div>

                                    </div>

                                    <div class="graph-node-outputs">
                                        <div class="graph-node-output" style="--row: 1">
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-socket">I</div>
                                            <div class="graph-node-output-label">Output</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </Content>
                        </Node>
                    </Block_NodeGraph>

                    <Block_Callout Type="construction">
                        <Icon><SvgSprite Link="/icons.svg?v=1#fluent-emoji-high-contrast--construction" Alt="Check" /></Icon>
                        <ChildContent>This section of my website is currently <b>under construction</b>.</ChildContent>
                    </Block_Callout>

                </OutlineSection>

            </Content>
        </Block_ArticleOutlined>
    </div>
</article>
